	<h1 class="title">紧跟美国，星巴克在中国19家门店推冰滴咖啡</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
